  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0d9a\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dad\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf \u0d85\u0db1\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The father of three who went to eat from the fuel station died in the accident",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police say that a father of three who had stopped his motorcycle near a petrol station in Buttala town and was walking home with a loaf of bread to get dinner, died on the spot after being hit by a motorcycle.",
        "The accident happened near a cloth shop near Rajapaksa Mawatha on Buttala Kataragama road.",
        "The deceased is a 45-year-old father of three named Vidyaratne Mathiyalage Vidyarathana, who was a retired soldier of the Army Engineer Corps.",
        "The motorcyclist who was driving the motorcycle that caused the accident is looking for whether he was on the ground."
      ],
